==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subscriber
<hw>Sub*scrib"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who subscribes; one who contributes to an undertaking by
subscribing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who enters his name for a paper, book, map, or
the like.</def> <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subscript</ent>⟦br⟧
